	<Title>
		Rx check: Do you know what you&apos;re taking?
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;When your doctor prescribes a medication, make sure you know the basics. Ask your doctor or pharmacist: 1. What are the brand and generic names of the medication? 2. Why do I need the medication? 3. How soon can I expect results? 4. When should I take the medication and for how long? 5. What are the side effects? 6. What if I miss a dose? 7. Are there any restrictions?&lt;/p&gt;
	</Body>
